<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10495</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20614</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克笑着向食人魔的妻子挥了挥手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20614</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26582</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“走开，小孩儿！”女人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克走近时，女人眨了眨眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37828</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我记得你！”她大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37828</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41555</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那天我给了你早饭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41555</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47215</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>后来我丈夫的一袋金币就不见了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47215</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51232</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔的妻子瞪着杰克。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56271</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那些金币不是不见了，”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56271</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是有人偷走了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯......”杰克故意慢慢地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以告诉你金币的事情。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77989</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不过......”他摸了摸肚子，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77989</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84426</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我太饿了，一个字也说不出来了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84426</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哼！”食人魔的妻子瞪着杰克。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96157</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是杰克看得出来她很好奇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96157</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108617</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女人叹了一口气，带杰克进去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108617</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112749</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她又给了杰克一碗热腾腾的粥。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112749</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115461</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给！”她生气地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115461</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125297</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快吃！吃完告诉我那些金币去哪儿了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125297</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克拿起勺子开始吃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149106</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161013</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他故意慢慢地喝着茶，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161013</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168858</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后慢慢地用纸巾擦了擦嘴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174683</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以......发生什么事了吗？” 杰克问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174683</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“食人魔有没有抓到......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180349</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咚！咚！咚！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180349</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>房子开始震动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187892</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太好了！”杰克心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187892</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191538</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克低下头，偷偷地笑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191538</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔回来了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
